text: Brigitte Boccone-Pagès is a Monegasque politician. She was elected as the vice president of the National Council on 22 February 2018. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Monegasque women in politics Category:21st- century women politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Members of the National Council (Monaco)
